January.title: DeltaHacks
January.notes: DeltaHacks is an annual hackathon that takes place at McMaster University. Our event, as the name, 'Delta', originates from social impact and social change. As a result, we strive to have social change related projects, by inviting professionals from all different industries (healthcare, science, etc) to pitch ideas for students to work on.

January.title: ConUHacks
January.notes: ConUHacks is open to all university students that have a passion for creating things with technology!
